WEBVTT

00:07.520 --> 00:08.920
‎SAY NO TO PIRACY, SUPPORT ORIGINALS

01:39.640 --> 01:42.960
‎ADAPTED FROM XI XING’S NOVEL
<i>‎QUEEN CHU</i>‎ ON QIDIAN.COM

01:43.600 --> 01:45.960
‎EPISODE TITLE

01:46.560 --> 01:47.920
INK AND BAMBOO SLIPS

01:48.000 --> 01:49.000
BROCADE AND SILK

01:49.840 --> 01:51.000
<i>In the previous life,</i>

01:51.080 --> 01:53.480
<i>the Anping Rebellion</i>
<i>erupted 25 days later,</i>

01:53.560 --> 01:55.680
<i>on the very day of my wedding next month.</i>

01:56.280 --> 01:58.880
<i>Should the wedding have never taken place,</i>

01:59.400 --> 02:05.000
<i>could the two princes have survived</i>
<i>and the rebellion been avoided entirely?</i>

02:06.600 --> 02:07.560
Next.

02:07.640 --> 02:09.400
<i>Sir, I've only got some herbs.</i>

02:09.479 --> 02:10.639
Keep the rhythm in mind.

02:10.720 --> 02:11.840
-Just like this.
-Next. Move quickly.

02:17.920 --> 02:19.440
<i>It's him.</i>

02:23.200 --> 02:24.040
Fu Jiu.

02:26.200 --> 02:27.400
Why haven't you returned to Yunzhong?

02:29.200 --> 02:32.360
I'm under the General's orders
to escort your dowry.

02:32.880 --> 02:34.520
I'll head back once the wedding is over.

02:35.120 --> 02:37.120
Can you take me away from here?

02:39.320 --> 02:40.360
Right now.

02:44.400 --> 02:46.200
I only take orders from the General.

02:59.800 --> 03:01.880
Are you in trouble?

03:13.280 --> 03:14.440
No.

03:24.800 --> 03:31.600
‎QINGYUN PAVILION

03:31.680 --> 03:33.560
I'm staying at the guesthouse.

03:33.640 --> 03:36.440
If you need anything, just let me know.

03:41.920 --> 03:44.520
Miss, what's come over you?

03:44.600 --> 03:46.080
His Highness favors you so much.

03:46.160 --> 03:47.280
Gifts piled mountain-high.

03:47.360 --> 03:48.600
The wedding is just days away.

03:48.680 --> 03:49.760
Why the sudden change of heart?

03:49.840 --> 03:52.240
If you miss the General,
we can always write to him.

03:52.320 --> 03:53.400
I have to go back.

03:55.720 --> 03:59.320
I need to see my father.

04:00.680 --> 04:03.040
<i>I am surrounded by Xiao Xun's eyes.</i>

04:03.560 --> 04:05.680
<i>I must find a way out.</i>

04:06.880 --> 04:11.000
<i>Never again</i>
<i>will I let history repeat itself.</i>

04:11.080 --> 04:14.760
GAOYANG COUNTY

04:26.400 --> 04:28.120
Xie Yanlai, going by the name Fu Jiu,

04:28.200 --> 04:31.360
is now in the Capital
as one of Chu Ling's retainers.

04:31.440 --> 04:34.000
My dear brother is truly something,

04:34.080 --> 04:36.280
trusted enough by the General

04:36.880 --> 04:39.000
to escort his beloved daughter's dowry.

04:39.600 --> 04:40.800
What of Chu Ling?

04:40.880 --> 04:43.280
Before a century-old lineage
like the Xie clan,

04:43.360 --> 04:44.960
he is but a lowly general.

04:45.040 --> 04:48.440
Your eldest sister is the Crown Princess,
with a son for the throne.

04:48.520 --> 04:51.080
-Your clout in the court--
-Watch your tongue.

04:51.160 --> 04:54.320
XIE YANFANG, PRIME MINISTER OF CHU

04:55.560 --> 04:59.080
Though my family
once had several grand chancellors,

04:59.600 --> 05:02.080
we remained outsiders
to the Capital's nobility.

05:02.680 --> 05:04.800
Five years ago,
I used my failing health as an excuse

05:04.880 --> 05:06.400
and moved back to Gaoyang,

05:07.360 --> 05:09.400
all to give His Majesty peace of mind.

05:10.520 --> 05:11.400
And yet you,

05:12.000 --> 05:15.640
after all this time at my side,
still haven't learned to hold your tongue.

05:16.840 --> 05:18.320
My apologies, sir.

05:18.400 --> 05:19.560
Please forgive me.

05:20.880 --> 05:25.080
I fear his spending too much time
with Chu Ling

05:25.640 --> 05:27.880
has swayed his loyalty.

05:28.840 --> 05:30.920
Five years without a firm hand,

05:31.440 --> 05:33.960
and even the most obedient
will start to forget themselves.

05:35.360 --> 05:39.680
Once he returns,
I'll dull his bite and clip his wings.

05:40.520 --> 05:41.760
He'll learn.

05:43.840 --> 05:48.040
My hound
never bites the hand that raised it.

05:48.120 --> 05:50.240
As for Xiao Xun…

05:51.400 --> 05:55.800
With his wedding so near,
we might as well drop in for a drink.

05:57.600 --> 06:00.880
Your Highness, our spies report
Xie Yanfang is readying his carriage

06:00.960 --> 06:02.320
and looks to be heading out.

06:02.400 --> 06:07.400
He retreated to Gaoyang
on the grounds of poor health

06:07.920 --> 06:09.000
five years ago,

06:09.600 --> 06:15.560
keeping himself
within easy reach of the Capital.

06:15.640 --> 06:17.960
When Chu Ling was exiled,

06:18.040 --> 06:19.680
the Xie family wasted no time
seizing what they could,

06:19.760 --> 06:22.800
planting their own people
throughout the ministries.

06:22.880 --> 06:25.920
Now, seeing the two princes
at each other's throats,

06:26.000 --> 06:27.960
are they looking to swoop in like us?

06:28.040 --> 06:29.960
Easier said

06:31.480 --> 06:32.840
than done.

06:33.760 --> 06:35.560
Tie Ying.

06:37.440 --> 06:39.520
There is something I cannot make sense of.

06:41.320 --> 06:45.560
Why the sudden frost from Zhao?

06:46.200 --> 06:49.480
Has the loose tongue of someone

06:51.240 --> 06:52.760
alerted her?

06:54.360 --> 06:56.600
My loyalty to you is absolute.

07:01.080 --> 07:02.240
Enough.

07:03.200 --> 07:04.040
Rise.

07:04.640 --> 07:06.400
I know where you stand.

07:07.560 --> 07:13.720
But given this sudden turn,
we can no longer afford to wait.

07:14.400 --> 07:17.840
Tomorrow, we'll use the Third Prince
to remove the Crown Prince.

07:17.920 --> 07:23.640
His fall will drive the other to revolt,
and I will be there to restore order.

07:23.720 --> 07:26.560
But Zhao is a wild card.

07:26.640 --> 07:29.640
The longer we wait, the greater the risk.

07:53.440 --> 07:55.320
Le. What's happening?

07:55.920 --> 07:57.080
The Third Prince
has turned on the Crown Prince

07:57.160 --> 07:58.720
and staged a coup.

07:59.480 --> 08:02.200
<i>It was supposed to happen</i>
<i>on the wedding day next month.</i>

08:02.720 --> 08:04.320
<i>Why has it come early?</i>

08:09.160 --> 08:11.120
His Highness orders your protection.

08:11.200 --> 08:14.440
Please stay in the Chu Mansion
until further notice.

08:14.520 --> 08:16.360
ANPING REBELLION - PAST LIFE

08:16.440 --> 08:19.280
-Where is Xun?
-His Highness orders your protection.

08:19.360 --> 08:21.640
Please stay in the Chu Mansion.

08:25.400 --> 08:28.720
<i>It's starting exactly like the rebellion.</i>

08:51.280 --> 08:54.760
His brother, Chu Lan,
poisoned the eldest imperial grandson

08:54.840 --> 08:56.240
in the first year of Anping.

08:57.760 --> 08:59.400
Miss, what's wrong?

08:59.480 --> 09:00.800
Let's run.

09:00.880 --> 09:03.480
Le, go fetch Fu Jiu from the guesthouse.

09:03.560 --> 09:04.600
What about you?

09:04.680 --> 09:06.040
I'm saving the imperial grandson.

09:06.120 --> 09:07.880
Miss, your life is what matters.

09:07.960 --> 09:09.600
Why worry about the imperial grandson now?

09:09.680 --> 09:11.920
If he truly dies by my uncle's hand,

09:12.000 --> 09:14.240
when the reckoning comes,
none of my family will be spared.

09:14.320 --> 09:16.000
Le, go.

09:16.080 --> 09:17.840
-Hurry up.
-Understood.

09:25.920 --> 09:29.560
<i>If Uncle was truly the murderer,</i>

09:30.120 --> 09:33.040
<i>then wherever he is,</i>
<i>so is the imperial grandson.</i>

09:44.640 --> 09:46.120
CHU LAN, CHU ZHAO'S UNCLE

09:46.200 --> 09:50.600
<i>Turns out it was really him.</i>

09:51.160 --> 09:54.040
<i>He's been in Xiao Xun's pocket all along.</i>

09:54.800 --> 09:57.960
<i>So, the poisoning of the Crown Prince,</i>
<i>the seizure of the Third Prince,</i>

09:58.040 --> 10:00.640
<i>and the murder of the imperial grandson</i>
<i>were all Xiao Xun's doing.</i>

10:01.160 --> 10:04.360
<i>He was behind the rebellion</i>
<i>from the very start.</i>

10:09.880 --> 10:12.680
IMPERIAL ANCESTRAL TEMPLE

10:12.760 --> 10:16.040
Your Highness, the army is assembled
and awaits your command.

10:16.120 --> 10:18.760
Take your death-sworn
to the Crown Prince's place

10:18.840 --> 10:21.320
and slaughter every last soul.

10:21.920 --> 10:23.360
Yes, Your Highness.

10:23.440 --> 10:26.080
Once our forces
breach the imperial palace,

10:26.160 --> 10:28.720
the throne will have a new master.

10:31.240 --> 10:33.160
The Third Prince
poisoned the Crown Prince,

10:33.240 --> 10:34.120
massacred the Eastern Palace,

10:34.200 --> 10:36.960
plotted against the late Emperor,
and raised a rebellion.

10:37.040 --> 10:39.200
His crimes demand death!

10:41.560 --> 10:42.960
Rest assured, Your Highness.

10:43.760 --> 10:47.680
I shall hold the throne for you.

10:54.640 --> 10:57.600
Don't be afraid. I am Chu Zhao,
daughter of the Guard General, Chu Ling.

10:57.680 --> 10:58.520
Follow me.

10:58.600 --> 10:59.920
Silence.

11:00.000 --> 11:01.880
Xiao Xun massacred the Eastern Palace.
His crimes are unforgivable.

11:01.960 --> 11:04.600
As his betrothed,
you are definitely complicit.

11:04.680 --> 11:06.160
Do not come here playing the savior!

11:06.240 --> 11:09.400
I am pledged to him,
but my family serves only the Crown.

11:10.000 --> 11:12.840
You came to Chu Mansion in your extremity
because you know this to be true.

11:12.920 --> 11:13.760
Am I right?

11:16.680 --> 11:19.080
His Majesty tasked me
to guard His Highness

11:19.600 --> 11:22.240
and find Chu Lan here if danger arose.

11:22.320 --> 11:24.680
But where is he now?

11:24.760 --> 11:25.920
My uncle has taken ill.

11:26.000 --> 11:27.640
He bade me to bring you out
before he drifted away.

11:29.840 --> 11:32.720
My father holds
His Majesty's absolute trust.

11:33.320 --> 11:37.400
Xiao Xun's men are closing in,
and we are defenseless here.

11:37.480 --> 11:40.200
To wait is to surrender to them.

11:40.960 --> 11:43.440
Our only chance is to break out now.

11:44.200 --> 11:47.720
If… it isn't safe here,

11:48.240 --> 11:49.680
where's left to go?

11:50.720 --> 11:53.560
What can you possibly do?

11:59.240 --> 12:01.040
We're going to Yunzhong.

12:02.640 --> 12:06.600
To find my father,
the Guard General, Chu Ling.

12:23.000 --> 12:24.040
Mr. Fu.

12:25.200 --> 12:26.200
Mr. Fu.

12:28.480 --> 12:29.320
Where is Chu Zhao?

12:29.400 --> 12:32.640
She was off to save the imperial grandson,
yet there is no sign of her.

12:32.720 --> 12:34.000
She must have fled.

12:35.720 --> 12:37.400
Everyone, come with me and find Chu Zhao.

12:37.480 --> 12:38.640
I'm coming too.

12:39.160 --> 12:41.920
Stay here. You'll only slow me down.

12:44.800 --> 12:47.200
‎CHU MANSION

12:51.360 --> 12:52.560
The Flame Decree.

12:56.120 --> 12:58.800
Have someone set it off in an hour.

12:59.320 --> 13:00.720
Let's go.

13:06.240 --> 13:09.160
EASTERN PALACE

13:15.880 --> 13:17.880
Your Highness, we have swept the area.

13:17.960 --> 13:19.240
There are no survivors.

13:19.920 --> 13:22.560
How is Zhao? What of the Chu Mansion?

13:22.640 --> 13:24.360
We have men stationed there.

13:28.560 --> 13:30.000
Your Highness,

13:31.040 --> 13:35.600
I hope you and Yu will be reunited

13:36.280 --> 13:38.040
with the Crown Prince soon.

13:46.360 --> 13:47.960
This is not Xiao Yu.

13:58.720 --> 13:59.640
QINGYUN PAVILION

14:10.320 --> 14:11.160
Please rest assured.

14:11.240 --> 14:13.440
My father sent an escort with the dowry.

14:13.520 --> 14:15.240
I've sent word for them to come for us.

14:15.320 --> 14:17.760
-Okay.
-Check over there!

14:17.840 --> 14:21.560
Le, please find Jiu.

14:22.160 --> 14:23.520
Back then,

14:24.120 --> 14:27.280
Chu Ling built the Longwei Army for me,

14:27.360 --> 14:29.480
with fire as the call.

14:30.320 --> 14:34.160
Only the Flame Decree
could command their blade.

14:34.880 --> 14:40.120
He promised me that as long as they stood,

14:41.120 --> 14:44.320
I would never be in danger.

14:44.920 --> 14:46.640
He broke his word.

14:50.720 --> 14:52.560
He broke it.

15:35.480 --> 15:37.760
Your Highness,
why didn't you just stay put?

15:44.560 --> 15:48.040
With all this chaos,
I was honestly terrified

15:48.840 --> 15:52.640
and trying to find Xun
when I happened to run into His Highness.

15:53.240 --> 15:54.880
Tie Ying, good timing.

15:55.480 --> 15:58.520
Help me escort him back to the palace.

15:58.600 --> 15:59.880
I see.

16:00.480 --> 16:02.880
I'll have someone
take you back to the mansion.

16:03.600 --> 16:05.280
You may entrust him to me.

16:08.600 --> 16:11.040
He is far too shaken to leave my side.

16:12.560 --> 16:13.720
Where is Xun?

16:17.160 --> 16:19.360
Perhaps we can wait for him here.

16:19.440 --> 16:21.360
I must insist that you hand him over.

16:31.720 --> 16:33.360
Give him to me right now.

17:52.680 --> 17:54.400
What took you so long?

18:03.800 --> 18:07.560
Chu Zhao, I'm taking you back to Yunzhong.

18:08.560 --> 18:10.240
-Fall back.
-Wait.

18:14.120 --> 18:16.360
My orders leave no room for waiting.

18:16.880 --> 18:22.200
The General's orders
are to bring you back alive.

18:23.720 --> 18:25.640
Zhao, are you leaving?

18:25.720 --> 18:28.160
Aren't you going to take me
to my grandfather?

18:32.880 --> 18:36.000
What's your relationship with Xie Yanfang?

18:38.760 --> 18:39.760
Tell me.

18:42.280 --> 18:43.680
What…

18:45.920 --> 18:46.920
is your connection?

18:50.280 --> 18:51.800
Why does it matter?

18:52.560 --> 18:56.320
He is Xiao Yu, the late Crown Prince's son
and the sole heir to the throne.

18:58.360 --> 19:00.800
Fu Jiu, you must protect him.

19:00.880 --> 19:04.040
I follow military orders, not yours.

19:09.720 --> 19:10.880
A large force is closing in.

19:13.800 --> 19:15.480
-What are you doing?
-My orders are to get you out.

19:16.080 --> 19:18.200
-No one else is my concern.
-What about him?

19:18.280 --> 19:21.240
If he is meant to survive, it will be so.

19:21.320 --> 19:24.800
If not, there is no point dying for him.

19:25.640 --> 19:27.840
-Stay here and keep him safe.
-Yes.

19:29.800 --> 19:30.960
Zhao!

19:36.520 --> 19:39.320
<i>Back then, Jiu got me</i>
<i>out of here just like this.</i>

19:43.680 --> 19:45.160
ANPING REBELLION - PAST LIFE

19:47.800 --> 19:49.680
Stop. Put me down.

19:49.760 --> 19:50.800
I have to find Xun.

19:50.880 --> 19:54.000
I am charged
with your safe return to Yunzhong.

19:55.680 --> 19:58.560
I am charged
with your safe return to Yunzhong.

20:00.080 --> 20:02.000
<i>I cannot let Xiao Xun take the throne.</i>

20:11.040 --> 20:12.800
Chu Zhao, have you lost your mind?

20:13.400 --> 20:14.920
-I have to go back.
-Not a chance!

20:16.920 --> 20:17.760
Move.

20:19.640 --> 20:23.560
Fu Jiu, you must keep me alive,
or you'll be disobeying orders.

20:56.760 --> 20:59.240
-This way. Hurry!
-Here!

21:00.640 --> 21:01.600
Zhao.

21:43.240 --> 21:47.040
NOBLE VIRTUE, ENDURING GRACE

21:50.440 --> 21:53.360
Follow me and protect His Majesty.

21:53.440 --> 21:54.520
-Yes!
-Yes!

22:04.360 --> 22:05.560
There are more of them coming.

22:06.080 --> 22:07.160
What do we do?

22:07.240 --> 22:08.240
‎Don't worry.

22:09.200 --> 22:11.720
I'll die before you do.

22:15.920 --> 22:19.160
‎Kill!

22:45.000 --> 22:46.640
He's here.

22:47.160 --> 22:50.320
By my order, comb the city.

22:50.400 --> 22:53.520
Anyone resembling the imperial grandson
is to be killed on sight.

22:53.600 --> 22:56.760
The rest of you,
follow me into the palace!

23:21.960 --> 23:23.040
Excuse me.

23:23.640 --> 23:25.040
Who set off the Flame Decree?

23:25.120 --> 23:26.320
I did.

23:26.400 --> 23:30.520
The Longwei Army has existed
for over a decade,

23:30.600 --> 23:32.640
yet this is the first time I have seen it.

23:33.720 --> 23:36.760
So my father commands
not only the frontier troops,

23:37.480 --> 23:39.320
but also this secret army.

23:41.600 --> 23:43.240
So this is the army

23:44.440 --> 23:45.360
he mentioned.

23:50.640 --> 23:51.560
This is the Flame Decree.

23:51.640 --> 23:53.760
It commands a secret army.

23:53.840 --> 23:55.640
The late Emperor
had me train them in secret,

23:55.720 --> 23:57.000
just for times like this.

23:58.200 --> 24:02.400
They will help you
protect the Capital and Zhao.

24:08.040 --> 24:13.280
With them on our side,
leaving here just got a little easier.

24:13.880 --> 24:18.240
<i>Last time, Xiao Xun marched on the palace</i>
<i>and the decree was never set off.</i>

24:18.320 --> 24:20.520
<i>The army stayed unknown to anyone.</i>

24:21.040 --> 24:25.880
<i>But now, they are my hand</i>
<i>to play against his bid for the throne.</i>

24:25.960 --> 24:27.640
-Scouts.
-Yes!

24:31.320 --> 24:32.920
Go and clear the path.

24:33.000 --> 24:34.440
Try to avoid the Lord of Xiaonan's men.

24:35.160 --> 24:37.920
The rest of you,
follow me out of the city now!

24:38.000 --> 24:38.840
-Yes!
-Yes!

24:38.920 --> 24:39.800
No, wait.

24:43.440 --> 24:46.640
With the army behind us,
there is no need to flee.

24:47.920 --> 24:48.760
Where are you going?

25:01.440 --> 25:02.920
To the palace.

25:08.120 --> 25:11.960
Your Majesty,
with both the princes fallen,

25:12.040 --> 25:15.200
the heir to the Lord of Xiaonan
is coming soon to protect Your Majesty.

25:15.280 --> 25:17.000
DENG YI, ATTENDANT CENSOR

25:17.080 --> 25:20.920
Your Majesty, you must act now.

25:21.000 --> 25:26.960
This brother of mine
was always the patient one.

25:27.040 --> 25:28.680
Yet now,

25:30.000 --> 25:33.040
even he reached his breaking point.

25:34.080 --> 25:35.560
Tell me,

25:36.080 --> 25:41.200
who is truly fit to inherit my throne?

25:42.280 --> 25:44.800
Your Majesty, is the one you have in mind

25:45.680 --> 25:49.040
the Lord of Xiaonan or his son?

25:59.440 --> 26:04.920
After all these years,
you still know me better than anyone.

26:06.760 --> 26:09.920
Go… and draft the decree.

26:11.800 --> 26:12.840
Yes, Your Majesty.

26:34.760 --> 26:36.920
We are escorting
His Highness back to the palace.

26:37.000 --> 26:37.960
Open the gates at once.

26:38.680 --> 26:39.840
He is an impostor.

26:40.520 --> 26:41.680
His life is forfeit.

26:41.760 --> 26:44.000
On my command, cut him down on sight!

27:02.520 --> 27:05.960
Your commander has committed treason
and been executed!

27:07.000 --> 27:10.240
Redeem yourselves now
and all will be forgiven.

27:10.840 --> 27:13.880
Those who resist will be slain!

27:40.200 --> 27:42.200
Can we win a head-on fight?

27:42.960 --> 27:44.600
The gates will fail.

27:45.200 --> 27:46.760
It's only a matter of time.

27:47.760 --> 27:51.160
The moment Xiao Xun enters the city,
the first one he'll kill is him.

27:51.920 --> 27:54.640
The second will be you.

27:59.400 --> 28:02.880
<i>Was that really him who just charged in?</i>

28:03.480 --> 28:04.360
Ram the gates.

28:15.320 --> 28:16.160
Is it worth it?

28:18.320 --> 28:19.480
Worth a try.

28:22.520 --> 28:23.400
Very well.

28:24.640 --> 28:29.640
We shall hold the gates as commanded,
even unto death.

28:38.400 --> 28:39.320
Jiu.

28:40.200 --> 28:41.280
Take care.

29:07.400 --> 29:10.960
As the General said,
if the gates fall, we are no soldiers.

29:11.680 --> 29:15.200
If we are to die today,
let it be at these very gates!

29:15.280 --> 29:17.360
-No retreat!
-No retreat!

29:17.440 --> 29:19.080
-No retreat!
-No retreat!

29:19.160 --> 29:20.960
-No retreat!
-No retreat!

29:21.040 --> 29:23.400
-No retreat!
-No retreat!

29:38.080 --> 29:39.920
GAOYANG COUNTY

29:40.000 --> 29:41.880
Xiao Xun is truly without mercy.

29:41.960 --> 29:44.760
The entire Eastern Palace
has been massacred.

29:44.840 --> 29:46.400
Even the Crown Princess and her son were…

29:50.560 --> 29:52.520
Nothing is more real

29:55.480 --> 29:57.400
than blade and blood.

29:59.680 --> 30:01.560
The throne of the State of Chu

30:02.280 --> 30:06.200
shall never belong to Xiao Xun.

30:11.160 --> 30:16.280
Du Qi, muster the troops
and head to the Capital.

30:22.440 --> 30:24.640
Your Highness, I have failed you.

30:25.360 --> 30:29.200
I was careless
to have underestimated Chu Ling.

30:30.760 --> 30:33.520
Her Ladyship took the imperial grandson.

30:38.360 --> 30:39.200
Zhao.

30:40.200 --> 30:42.080
You've found something out after all.

30:50.160 --> 30:53.080
Anyone entering unsummoned shall die.

30:53.680 --> 30:56.280
I am Chu Zhao, daughter of Chu Ling,
the Guard General of Yunzhong.

30:56.360 --> 30:59.040
I have escorted His Highness back
and request an audience.

31:08.000 --> 31:12.120
TAIJI HALL

31:33.680 --> 31:34.520
Deng Yi?

31:36.120 --> 31:37.800
You know me?

31:37.880 --> 31:41.720
<i>You were the Grand Mentor,</i>
<i>the person Xiao Xun trusted most.</i>

31:42.320 --> 31:44.200
<i>Of course I do.</i>

31:47.200 --> 31:48.480
<i>It is plain to see</i>

31:49.120 --> 31:51.720
<i>Deng Yi must have had a hand</i>
<i>in the rebellion.</i>

31:53.400 --> 31:58.400
You and I have met before.

32:15.800 --> 32:18.800
Greetings, Your Highness.

32:23.640 --> 32:27.080
His Majesty is unwell
and cannot receive you.

32:32.720 --> 32:35.560
Your brush tells quite a crooked tale.

32:36.440 --> 32:38.640
Shall I charge your clan

32:39.600 --> 32:43.320
with treason with my brush
for tonight's trespass?

32:44.720 --> 32:46.440
What did Xiao Xun promise you?

32:47.120 --> 32:50.640
The Nine Bestowments
or the first honors for backing his rise?

32:52.400 --> 32:54.280
The Crown Prince's heir stands before you.

32:55.200 --> 33:00.280
Which do you think
leaves a finer mark in history?

33:00.800 --> 33:04.320
Kingmaking for a usurper
or guiding a young emperor to glory?

33:06.880 --> 33:09.600
And do you believe
Xiao Xun, once enthroned,

33:09.680 --> 33:12.440
would spare a historian
who knows the truth

33:12.520 --> 33:13.800
of how he seized power?

33:17.000 --> 33:18.880
But if His Highness takes the throne,

33:18.960 --> 33:20.960
you will be
the founding pillar of his reign,

33:21.040 --> 33:22.760
first among all ministers,

33:22.840 --> 33:26.120
with every word of history yours to write.

33:40.120 --> 33:41.320
Miss Chu,

33:42.320 --> 33:45.640
please escort His Highness to the Emperor.

33:55.560 --> 33:58.440
TAIJI HALL

34:00.320 --> 34:02.520
-Your Highness.
-I am Yu.

34:03.440 --> 34:04.280
Alright.

34:04.800 --> 34:07.840
Yu, from now on,

34:08.480 --> 34:12.159
our lives are bound together.

34:13.960 --> 34:17.719
My father is the person
His Majesty trusted most.

34:18.320 --> 34:22.360
And I want to be that person for you.

34:22.960 --> 34:24.800
You will always be the one I trust most.

35:17.360 --> 35:18.200
Your Majesty,

35:18.280 --> 35:22.000
Chu Zhao, daughter of Chu Ling,
has escorted His Highness back.

35:26.960 --> 35:29.480
I, Chu Zhao, daughter of Chu Ling,
the Guard General of Yunzhong,

35:29.560 --> 35:31.040
pay my respects to Your Majesty.

35:37.320 --> 35:41.920
Like father, like daughter.

35:42.000 --> 35:46.800
Bold beyond measure
and utterly without restraint.

35:48.320 --> 35:52.120
Your Majesty, the trespass
was never my wish.

35:52.720 --> 35:55.520
Mr. Qi brought His Highness
to my place for refuge,

35:55.600 --> 35:58.160
and my father's men happened
to be in the Capital.

35:58.240 --> 35:59.080
In that dire hour,

35:59.160 --> 36:02.160
I mobilized the Longwei Army
to guard the throne

36:03.000 --> 36:05.920
and ensure the safe return
of His Highness.

36:08.880 --> 36:10.280
Rise.

36:22.960 --> 36:24.400
Grandfather.

36:36.320 --> 36:40.840
I sent him away to keep him safe.

36:41.920 --> 36:46.280
And now you bring him back
to this very danger.

36:46.360 --> 36:50.400
What is your intent?

36:51.120 --> 36:56.040
Your Majesty, Xiao Xun
plotted against the princes,

36:56.120 --> 37:00.000
hunted your grandson,
and harbors treason against Your Majesty.

37:00.080 --> 37:02.880
Though betrothed to him,

37:02.960 --> 37:05.520
I will not stand by
and watch a traitor run rampant.

37:08.400 --> 37:09.240
Imperial Physician!

37:13.800 --> 37:16.800
Do not be afraid. He will be fine.

37:21.080 --> 37:23.400
<i>If His Majesty were to die now,</i>

37:23.480 --> 37:28.200
<i>not only would I fail to stop Xiao Xun,</i>
<i>but he would frame me for regicide.</i>

37:28.280 --> 37:31.920
<i>Everything I have fought for</i>
<i>would be lost.</i>

37:35.080 --> 37:36.280
We can't hold much longer!

37:36.360 --> 37:38.600
Get Miss Chu out of here!

37:38.680 --> 37:41.160
With that tally, they won't stop you!

37:42.720 --> 37:44.320
Hold on!

37:44.400 --> 37:45.640
Stand firm!

37:50.520 --> 37:52.400
See?

37:53.640 --> 37:56.600
I am poisoned and will not see the dawn.

37:57.520 --> 38:01.600
The decree of succession is already drawn.

38:02.160 --> 38:03.680
By daybreak,

38:04.800 --> 38:07.720
Xiao Xun will be the new emperor.

38:09.720 --> 38:12.640
Deng Yi will escort you both to safety.

38:15.200 --> 38:16.120
Your Majesty,

38:16.640 --> 38:19.800
would you truly hand this realm over
to the Lord of Xiaonan and his son?

38:19.880 --> 38:23.920
Can a child of six hold the throne?

38:26.880 --> 38:27.720
Let it be.

38:28.720 --> 38:30.920
Now that it has come to this,

38:31.520 --> 38:35.320
as long as a Xiao sits upon the throne,

38:36.160 --> 38:42.120
I can meet my ancestors with a clear soul.

38:42.880 --> 38:44.200
But Your Majesty,

38:44.280 --> 38:47.600
if His Highness goes to the border,
what is my father to do?

38:48.680 --> 38:52.600
Carve out his own territory
and defy the new emperor

38:53.120 --> 38:54.960
just to protect him?

38:55.480 --> 39:01.720
The troops under your father's command
need not be involved.

39:02.400 --> 39:03.840
The Longwei Army,

39:03.920 --> 39:06.920
spread across the land,
is enough to keep him safe.

39:07.000 --> 39:07.960
Your Majesty,

39:08.720 --> 39:10.960
willing or not, my father

39:11.040 --> 39:13.400
will be seen as a threat
to the new emperor regardless.

39:14.000 --> 39:18.280
If you trust him
to keep your grandson safe at the border,

39:18.880 --> 39:20.560
why don't you believe

39:20.640 --> 39:23.080
that he can protect His Highness
holding the throne?

39:27.760 --> 39:31.120
The last thing your father would ever want

39:31.800 --> 39:35.120
is to hold this realm together for me.

39:48.520 --> 39:52.560
You have reminded me of something.

39:53.080 --> 39:56.720
If Xiao Xun insists on marrying you,

39:56.800 --> 40:00.800
your father would not stand against him,

40:00.880 --> 40:05.440
and his troops would become a threat.

40:05.520 --> 40:06.800
It seems

40:08.880 --> 40:09.880
I cannot let you leave either.

40:34.240 --> 40:37.320
As commanded, whoever kills Chu Zhao

40:37.920 --> 40:39.400
dies by my hand.

40:41.440 --> 40:42.320
Insolence!

40:42.840 --> 40:46.120
You would risk your entire clan
to commit such blatant treason?

40:48.280 --> 40:49.960
I would welcome it.

41:05.800 --> 41:08.240
-Go ahead.
-Then we die together!

41:08.320 --> 41:09.480
Jiu.

41:19.320 --> 41:22.280
Your Majesty, please let me
be your grandson's elder sister,

41:23.720 --> 41:24.960
the Grand Princess

41:26.480 --> 41:28.440
of the State of Chu,

41:32.080 --> 41:33.960
and help him

41:35.200 --> 41:36.720
hold the throne.

41:36.800 --> 41:37.960
What did you say?

41:38.040 --> 41:42.240
I know you and my father
were sworn brothers

41:42.320 --> 41:44.360
before you took the throne.

41:45.680 --> 41:49.720
My title as the Grand Princess
would make my father kin,

41:49.800 --> 41:51.320
not just a subject to your grandson.

41:52.160 --> 41:56.120
And the frontier troops
and the Longwei Army

41:56.920 --> 41:59.120
become guardians for us both.

42:02.400 --> 42:03.600
So,

42:04.800 --> 42:09.080
that is His Highness's greatest advantage
in holding the throne.

42:10.640 --> 42:12.760
I may be dying,

42:12.840 --> 42:19.160
but I've still got enough breath
to kill you and your father,

42:19.240 --> 42:22.280
a plague upon this throne.

42:22.360 --> 42:26.640
Then why not spend it
securing a future for the realm?

42:27.720 --> 42:31.480
Xiao Xun's ascension
would invite unrest and rebellion

42:31.560 --> 42:34.000
and even invasion
from the Northern Desert.

42:35.240 --> 42:36.480
By then,

42:37.080 --> 42:41.600
the people will be consumed by endless war
and everything will be lost.

42:42.560 --> 42:44.520
How will you ever be able

42:44.600 --> 42:49.760
to face your ancestors
with a clear conscience in the afterlife?

43:02.480 --> 43:04.120
The Grand Princess

43:05.720 --> 43:07.840
of the realm…

43:09.600 --> 43:10.880
Please rest assured.

43:11.400 --> 43:15.440
This title begins with me
and ends with me.

43:16.080 --> 43:18.360
So long as I hold it,

43:18.440 --> 43:21.560
I take no husband, and I bear no child.

43:21.640 --> 43:24.760
I yield my power to no one,

43:24.840 --> 43:26.480
and I shield no one with my shadow.

43:27.000 --> 43:31.440
Should I break this oath,
I shall be marked a traitor,

43:31.520 --> 43:34.040
and let everyone be my executioner.

43:35.520 --> 43:38.080
I can wield a blade against enemies

43:39.120 --> 43:42.720
and cut every tie that reaches
for the imperial seal.

43:44.080 --> 43:47.800
What I desire is for the annals
of history to record,

43:49.400 --> 43:51.960
"Chu Zhao, the Grand Princess
of the State of Chu,

43:52.040 --> 43:53.600
remained unwed for life.

43:55.120 --> 43:59.480
She rests beside her father,
Chu Ling, at the border."

44:05.560 --> 44:09.320
TAIJI HALL

44:22.280 --> 44:27.760
I, Xiao Xun, heir to the Lord of Xiaonan
request to attend upon Your Majesty!

45:06.120 --> 45:09.680
The Third Prince, Xiao Zhu,
committed treason, murdered his brother,

45:10.280 --> 45:12.480
and massacred the Capital
in a bid for the throne.

45:12.560 --> 45:14.320
This cannot go unpunished.

45:14.400 --> 45:16.760
He is stripped of his title
and reduced to commoner status,

45:16.840 --> 45:20.080
and his maternal clan,
the Zhao clan, meets extermination.

45:20.160 --> 45:23.720
Xiao Xun, heir to the Lord of Xiaonan,
defended the throne with distinction

45:23.800 --> 45:25.920
and honored the imperial line.

45:29.200 --> 45:30.480
Your Highness.

45:31.200 --> 45:32.480
Please receive the decree.

45:39.080 --> 45:43.760
We, the Xie clan, have come
to your aid, Your Majesty.

45:56.600 --> 45:57.560
It's him.

46:03.680 --> 46:07.200
The stars bring ill omens,
and traitors breed chaos.

46:07.280 --> 46:08.560
Both of my sons have fallen.

46:09.160 --> 46:11.560
It is by the valor and wit of Chu Zhao,
daughter of Chu Ling,

46:11.640 --> 46:16.760
who rode armed to deliver
the imperial grandson to safety,

46:16.840 --> 46:20.400
that the Xiao ancestral line endures.

46:20.480 --> 46:22.920
Chu Ling and I once shared
the dust and blood of battle

46:23.000 --> 46:26.040
and swore a brother's oath.

46:26.640 --> 46:28.720
For the eternal stability of the realm,

46:28.800 --> 46:31.320
I hereby pass the throne

46:35.120 --> 46:37.240
to my eldest imperial grandson, Xiao Yu.

46:43.760 --> 46:47.640
And I confer the title
of Grand Princess upon Chu Zhao.

46:47.720 --> 46:51.560
Her betrothal to Xiao Xun
is hereby severed.
